nodes.text: The Rock-eater was a vorantikus living on Voss during the Galactic War. It was slain in the Pelath-Ri Marches.

The Rock-eater appears in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic as a Champion boss on the planet Voss. It is the final encounter of the heroic mission Rock-Eaters. This article assumes 100% game completion, which means he was killed.
